# Changelog (Fastlane / store metadata)

This project should track release notes in Fastlane-style metadata:

- `fastlane/metadata/android/en-US/changelogs/<versionCode>.txt`

Rules:

- Whenever `versionCode` is bumped in `app/build.gradle.kts`, add a matching changelog file named exactly `<versionCode>.txt`.
- Changelog entries must be **English**, short and user-facing (**2–10 lines**).
- The changelog MUST describe the actual shipped changes (no generic filler).
- Prefer one change per line with prefixes:
  - `- Fix: …`
  - `- Add: …`
  - `- Change: …`
  - `- Security: …`

